      "category": "Gastrointestinal - EMERGENCY",
      "description": "A rabbit refusing food or showing reduced appetite is a TRUE EMERGENCY. Rabbits' digestive systems require constant movement; without food, gut bacteria balance changes within hours, causing potentially fatal GI stasis.",
